channel.description:
Yes, I am looking for a development team for my 317 server. I need a team so we can all get this done, you will probably most be likely be accepted for a position if you apply. These are the current positions you can apply for;
[b][u]Insanity Online Forum Mod(s)[/u][/b] Xufet Java is on my Pancake Tacoboyy [font=Verdana][i]Note: Forum moderators may be demoted due to to many moderators and current behaviour. If one of the admins decide you have to go and have a good explanatory reason they must forward it on to me first and get acceptance. You will be then told the reason why and demoted ASAP.[/i][/font]
[u][b]BETA Testers[/b][/u] P I M P 3 D Tut Mod_zez Djayboi6
[u][b]Website Coder[/b][/u] hipandpeanut butter
[u][b]Server Coder[/b][/u] Darkning Rash
Here are the applications;
[b][u]Our Forum Mods[/u][/b] [b]CLOSED[/b]
[u][b]Server Coder[/b][/u] [b]CLOSED[/b]
[b][u]Server BETA Tester[/u][/b] [code]Name: Have you ever Beta Tested a server before: What will you Beta test on the server(skills, features, other): Join our forums? (You get ranked as Beta Tester):[/code]
[b][u]Client Coder[/u][/b] [code]Name: Experience with Client coding (include example): Are you compatible with making a 317 client: Do you make custom models & implement to client?: Have you ever made a client for a server?: How long have you been coding clients for?: Age?: [/code]
[u][b]Website Coder[/b][/u] [b]CLOSED[/b]
Fill those Applications out above if you would like to apply for a position that is available, so far all of them are open! So start APPLYING. The server is a 317, Devolution V7 Based, but redone by us and we will make it awesome. Also, Don't forget to join our forums which is located to my signature, their brand new so don't expect them to be flooded with posts.
[quote="Miss Silabsoft"]sure then you have my permission.[/quote]
